# Copy to .env (or .env.local) and fill in. Vite inlines VITE_* vars at build time.

# LINZ Basemaps Developer API key — enables the "High-detail NZ terrain (LINZ)" overlay, which layers
# LINZ 1 m LIDAR DEM over the AWS Terrarium baseline (see src/terrain/demTiles.ts). Free and
# non-expiring: request a site-restricted Developer key from basemaps@linz.govt.nz (the auto key from
# visiting basemaps.linz.govt.nz expires after ~90 days — don't use that for a deployed site). The key
# is public by design. Leave empty to keep the AWS Terrarium baseline only.
VITE_LINZ_API_KEY=
